Is it a fruit(common definition not botanical)? Is it commonly found on a sandwich? Does it grow on a tree? Does it grow underground? Can it be found in a pie? Is it mostly green? Does it grow on a bush? Is it usually round(on at least one axis)? Does it have seeds on the outside? ... Is it mostly yellow? Is it crunchy when raw? Is it usually larger than a softball? Would you cook it in a pan? Is it spicy? Are you allowed to have it in the Computer Science Building? Is it sour when ripe? Would you usually store it in a refrigerator? Does it grow on a vine? Could you find it in a salsa?
